      prompt: `<div>A train is traveling at a constant speed along a straight portion of railway. The equation d = 30t gives the distance d, in feet from a railway marker, that the train will be t seconds after passing the marker. How many feet from the marker will the train be 3 seconds after passing the marker?</div>`,
